task.summary: recommit after I messed up the repository...
Desktop items are now called through switch statement.
Fixed issue where files attributes was accidently renamed.
added working grid displaying data from a simple JavaScript data source
Renamed html class from markos-folder-container to markos-file-manager.
Merging of software templates are now handled by _SoftwareContainer.
Consolidated all module css in markos.css
Custom widgets now honor baseClass attribute. Created method to add template to _SoftwareContainer header.
system.json now gets loaded into a memory store with global access.
Project module can now display html template strings and embed iframes.
Added UAS in Local Government Story Map
Fixed issue with XML parser throwing errors and not being able to handle nested elements.
Fixed issue with month returning wrong number.
Fixed issue where max min icons were not update on toggle.
Changed header from id to label.
Fixed issue with overlap resize icon.
_SoftwareContainer can now be moved within window.
